## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6126d-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> 可能會停止回應時沒有環境交易和<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A>稱為和之後回復交易。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6126d-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> may hang when there is an ambient transaction and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> is called and afterwards the transaction is rolled back.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6126d-110">如果<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A>稱為之前完成的交易回復，競爭情形會存在，導致在呼叫<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A>停止回應。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6126d-110">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> is called prior to the transaction rollback completing, a race condition will exist, causing the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> to hang.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6126d-111">這可由下列虛擬程式碼範例說明</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6126d-111">This can be illustrated by the following pseudo-code example</span></span>  
  
```  
using (TransactionScope ts = new TransactionScope())   
{  
   try  
   {  
       rc.Complete();  
      ...  
   }  
   Catch (Exception)   
   {  
      rc.Abandon()  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6126d-112">這不是使用 T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RecieveContext 建議的模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6126d-112">This is not the recommended pattern for working with T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RecieveContext.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6126d-113">改為 try/catch 區塊應該放在交易範圍之外。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6126d-113">Instead the try/catch block should be placed outside of the transaction scope.</span></span>

